projecttitle: Development of organic farming and  social entreprenurship - TEMI community
project_descrip: Short: DEVELOPMENT OF ORGANIC FARMING AND  SOCIAL ENTREPRENURSHIP - TEMI COMMUNITY Long: The project aims to develop social entrepreneurship and organic farming in the Kakhet area, which contributes to the development of a cohesive society in Georgia. Our partner is the charitable association TEMI, which offers living and working place for nearly 80 people with special needs. Supported by Estonian expertise: sustainable irrigation systems and organic agricultural production and marketing will be developed in TEMI, to increase community income from entrepreneurship. Trainings with other (starting) organic producers on national, EU standards are organized as well as organic producers network and marketing will be developed.
